summary: Basic template, dawnguard+dragonborn main quests completed.
descriptionHtml:
Basic template, dawnguard+dragonborn main quests completed.
Vampire lord 3 points, it\'s primary focus is Melee. 
removed all OP weapons, and gear.
Enchanting, Blacksmith + alc are all -100 if i had it my way i completely removed it.

unfortunately i completed 1 quest, Dawnbreaker i was not at that time thinking about a template.
some other boring quests are also done, like companions *anyone done it a 100 times by now*
also notice weather was bugged, use console FW 81A. common problem when playing DLCs.

when saying Relics are missing, just load and save again will fix any problems.

Etherreal Elven Overhaul recommended.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24273/?

Hair is custom, so char will be bold, use Showracemenu
